{"tid":1653813,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"9名西班牙加泰獨派領袖囚9至13年　獨派團體揚言公民抗命","createTime":"2019-10-14T09:05:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T23:17:06.000Z","uid":37554,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3946531d3ffee4af1448b1cc37662e758a5cb525","tid":1653813,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T09:05:37.000Z","msg":"9名西班牙加泰羅尼亞地區的獨派領袖，因前年在加泰獨立運動中的角色，被西班牙最高法院判監9至13年。<br />\n<br />\n當中的加泰自治政府前副主席朱奎拉斯，被裁定煽動暴亂及挪用公款罪成，判囚13年。同案3名被告，被裁定不守法罪成，毋須入獄。<br />\n<br />\n案中全部12名被告都否認控罪，經審訊後被裁定罪成，他們分別是政客及社運人士。<br />\n<br />\n法庭判刑前，在加泰地區爭取獨立的團體揚言，假如任何一名被告被判囚，將會發起示威活動及公民抗命。西班牙當局加派數以百計警員到當地戒備。"},{"pid":"632445dd74849cc301a8c9209146f28b3eb18d8b","tid":1653813,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T09:09:18.000Z","msg":"當日公投大比數通過，佢地遲遲唔肯宣佈獨立，拖泥帶水令民氣消散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7bcb28cef0377ae868df7762499dd86d6c2f19","tid":1653813,"uid":34293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T09:11:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i1C08Tu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi1C08Tu.jpg&h=72679345&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96ec238ee58c94e6fcf7342d4ee216bd102429cd","tid":1653813,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T11:50:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486093-20191014.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486093-20191014.htm&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=e07e7ca1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486093-20191014.htm&h=7371869d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486093-20191014.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ca3ca19409363bd6c0d4e0303f6f9fa8488cac45","tid":1653813,"uid":13781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl